00041C00                            ; table at 0x041000-0x0418AB. Those table entries point monotonically into the larger
00041C00                            ; 0x041C00-0x07FF66 payload region; this first 0x8B0F-byte window now keeps the proven
00041C00                            ; ROM-order starts explicit instead of leaving the entire local-target body monolithic.
00041C00                            ;
00041C00                            ; The tagged front table now also proves that the isolated 0x045842 target belongs with the
00041C00                            ; later planar tile blocks rather than the surrounding irregular payload records, so that one
00041C00                            ; block now lives in its own graphics-oriented child module too.
