0004A70F                            ; ROM range: 0x04A70F-0x04E5A9
0004A70F                            ; Continued local-target payload window reached from the same flagged ROM-reference
0004A70F                            ; table at 0x041000-0x0418AB. This span now separates the irregular front records from
0004A70F                            ; the first long fixed-stride run at 0x04BFAA.
0004A70F                            ;
0004A70F                            ; That run is no longer treated as a generic payload stride family: each 0x4C0-byte record
0004A70F                            ; divides cleanly into 38 32-byte tiles and the byte planes read like 4bpp Mega Drive art,
0004A70F                            ; so the dedicated child module now records it as a planar tile family while the higher-level
0004A70F                            ; loader and asset owner remain open.
