0004BFAA                            ; ROM range: 0x04BFAA-0x04E5A9
0004BFAA                            ; Eight consecutive 0x4C0-byte planar tile blocks inside the bank040000 local-target payload
0004BFAA                            ; family.
0004BFAA                            ;
0004BFAA                            ; Each record is exactly 38 Mega Drive 4bpp tiles (0x26 * 0x20 bytes), and row-level byte
0004BFAA                            ; inspection shows the expected bitplane-style patterns rather than arbitrary control data.
0004BFAA                            ; The flagged ROM-reference table at 0x041000 lands on each start in order, so the graphics
0004BFAA                            ; ownership is strong even though the higher-level loader and asset purpose are still open.
