00099B00                            ; Later words in the following table point back into this lead-in, so keep it separate from
00099B00                            ; the offset list instead of hiding the whole block behind one anonymous incbin. The bytes
00099B00                            ; still only justify a structural word-band split, but that is enough to make the full
00099B00                            ; 0x099B00-0x09A347 pre-window command front source-visible in ROM order.
00099B00                            Bank080000_CommandLeadIn_099B00:
00099B00 58A5 B416 A8B2 AA4B ADA1+  	dc.w	$58A5,$B416,$A8B2,$AA4B,$ADA1,$B092,$BAFA,$BE7E
