00099B32                            ; data block. One word ($F7FD) still falls outside the local range, so keep the entries
00099B32                            ; literal instead of forcing stronger subsystem meaning. Those local targets now split the
00099B32                            ; command body into a short prelude plus narrower ROM-order record slices instead of one
00099B32                            ; monolithic trailing incbin.
